titles.title: A concurrent resolution relating to the enrollment of S. 1932.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 2/8/2006--Passed Senate without amendment. Deems the enrollment of S. 1932 (providing for reconciliation under the concurrent resolution on the budget for FY2006) as presented to the President for his signature on February 8, 2006, as the true enrollment of the bill reflecting the intent of Congress in enacting it into law.
